Package: mlLang
Type: Package
Title: Converter for the unified machine learning language
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2016-12-07
Authors@R: c(person("Andreas", "Frorath", email="froratha@informatik.uni-freiburg.de",
                    role=c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Stefan", "Feuerriegel", email="stefan.feuerriegel@is.uni-freiburg.de",
                    role=c("aut")))
Author: Andreas Frorath [aut,cre]
  Stefan Feuerriegel [aut]
Maintainer: Stefan Feuerriegel <stefan.feuerriegel@is.uni-freiburg.de>
Description: This package ships access to the unified machine learning language from inside R. For
  this purpose, it implements converters in two directions. (1) It automatically reads files in
  the unified machine learning language from custom XML files and then constructs a corresponding
  machine learning model in R. (2) It also supports the other direction an automatically converts
  machine learning models into XML files according to the unified machine learning language. All
  machine learning models are built on top of "caret".
